Property details

Nestled between downtown Santa Barbara and the desirable Mesa neighborhood, this single-level 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom condo is ideally located mere minutes from the beach, restaurants, shopping, and hiking trails. The unit overlooks Honda Valley Park with serene views of the natural, open space. Fresh... ly painted with new fixtures and carpeting, the condo is light and bright with an open-concept living area that opens to a spacious, private patio with new drought-tolerant landscaping and low maintenance drip irrigation.The Highlands HOA features two pools, spa, sauna, and onsite laundry facilities. The unit has one assigned carport space with storage cabinets. Great rental potential!
